Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要唱什麼歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要唱什麼好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 我也口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不唱歌嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是想交友才參加的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道是要參加聯誼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你害羞的話 我會陪你一起唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 選歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.48,Default-TOP,NTP,0,0,0,,等 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你這樣說的話 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更想使壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果變成這樣的話 該怎麼辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那男的途中就變成宇佐了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的性騷擾妄想一定有一百零八式的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我的妄想 妄想的對象也不想是其他男人
